{
  "stem": "18294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 171.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If not the smartest, we would [INAUDIBLE] might be in Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But how can you leave a home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother said, how can you leave a home?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've had all this all my life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could not going to leave everything there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And did you get much time from the time they said you have to run, you have to leave?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- I don't-- this I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not-- not really much time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't give you weeks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's time for area.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now you have to move it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So maybe there was a couple days because he couldn't come when said go to prepare ourselves to go out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the ghetto, there was a quarter of the town where the Jewish population was living, most of them there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where they took you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Took to there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, they make a fence around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, not a fence-- just they blocked up the windows which was going out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They blocked up with bricks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not to-- you're not to-- you can't go out there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, you can't see there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only what is in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was, I don't know exactly, maybe 10 or 15 streets like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were small streets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I find it when we arrived in the ghetto, the Gebietskommissar from the ghetto, provided with the ghetto, he had really give you the places to live.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He really give you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because of my father, he was work in such a proper way, very important place with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had a good place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was the Jewish commander was on this part of the yard where I was living.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- we had-- we was four girls and four boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody of us had a boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
